{"tid":1462852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機管局口裡不一 Airside如常運作","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:22:23.000Z","uid":68125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc0a0426201ac0dda657db187d6ecef61b280240","tid":1462852,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:26:40.000Z","msg":"以下內容轉自K&rsquo;s Aviation <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KSAviation1/photos/a.730162497186654/1082618878607679?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKSAviation1%2Fphotos%2Fa.730162497186654%2F1082618878607679%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=HBLsGxwPt4tNlCAdiZVEvqtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=3cbf2046\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KSAviation1/photos/a.730162497186654/1082618878607679?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n（不要輕信謠言）<br />\n外界有微博截圖指出由B-LRI執飛之CX899因為國泰航空 (CX) 方面未交機組名單，而不獲進入中國空域改而使用日本及台灣空域返港。<br />\n<br />\n事實是經求證後指出，是壞機轉降大阪關西機場 (KIX) ，之後改為今日抵港。而民航處昨日說明，除非已經進入香港飛行情報區，否則暫停起飛/可能要轉降其他機場。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚方面，雖然登記行段暫停，但是國泰航空 (CX) 空中服務員今晚需要報到。如無意外，跟昨晚一樣只會做轉機客。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n推！"},{"pid":"60a83530fd09207d51a9ae7c3c3ca7129addc95b","tid":1462852,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:30:32.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"f9dd2438796d09f84827af9c2548ed3d65b2eef7","tid":1462852,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:48:02.000Z","msg":"幫手推啊"},{"pid":"3b8cebdaa63587900a0cce8faa2ba414d3c40dfe","tid":1462852,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"推"}]}